sidered model.\n  For unrelated machines, an FPTAS for $R2|G = bipartite|C_{\\max}$ is provided.\nWe also show that there is no algorithm of approximation ratio\n$O(n^bp_{\\max}^{1-\\epsilon})$, even for $Rm|G = bipartite|C_{max}$ for $m \\ge\n3$ and any $\\epsilon > 0$, $b > 0$, unless $P = NP$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jun 2021 00:43:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-29"}
