}$ global polarizations should peak at the\nenergy range accessible to NICA and HADES.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jun 2021 03:21:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Mar 2022 19:14:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-28"}
