l is validated against exact solutions for\nseveral use-cases, including mechanically- and thermally-induced, inviscid and\nviscous detonations. Results indicate that the model can accurately simulate a\nvery broad range of problems involving the nonlinear interaction between\nreactive and inert materials within a single framework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jun 2021 08:52:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-03"}
