y function of 47 Tuc. No significant population that seems to belong\nto the globular cluster has been observed in the energy range of 0.5-2.0 keV\nusing eROSITA observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jun 2021 10:08:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Feb 2022 10:32:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-03"}
