ation of almost the whole\nstellar content of the Sco-Cen association will become possible once the final\nGaia and eROSITA catalogs are available by the end of this decade. We\nfurthermore call into question any source population classification scheme that\nrelies on purely kinematic selection criteria.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jun 2021 10:08:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-25"}
