performs a TensorRT optimized model on\nan Nvidia Jetson platform in both throughput and energy consumption.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jun 2021 14:45:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Oct 2021 13:22:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-22"}
