ated evaluation schemes. We also discuss the impact of\ncrowd workers on the results and show that the varying ability of crowd workers\ndoes not significantly impact the results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 27 Jun 2021 17:37:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 30 Aug 2021 14:10:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-31"}
